          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 43,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Then I pulverized them as the dust of the earth; I crushed and stamped them as the mire of the streets. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 43,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Then I pulverized them as the dust of the earth; I crushed and stamped them as the mire of the streets."
